OL,3,CFight to save children's services
OL,4,Ccentre arrives at council HQ
OL,6,FThe fight for the future of children's
OL,7,Fservice on the Isle of Sheppey was
OL,8,Fbrought to the front door of Kent
OL,9,FCounty Council.
OL,11,FMore than 6,000 people have signed a
OL,12,Fpetition calling on an abandonment of
OL,13,Fplans to stop funding the Seashells
OL,14,FChildren & Families Hub on the Isle of
OL,15,FSheppey.
OL,17,FThe petition was heard at a full
OL,18,Fcouncil meeting which took place on
OL,19,FThursday morning.
