OL,3,CFight to save children's services
OL,4,Ccentre arrives at council HQ
OL,6,FKent County Council said in light of
OL,7,Fthe significant financial pressures
OL,8,Fits facing, it is looking at how it
OL,9,Fdelivers services to ensure they are
OL,10,Fefficient and cost effective.
OL,12,FThe council says that after
OL,13,Fimplementing its own Family Hub
OL,14,Fservices last year, managing the costs
OL,15,Ffor both those and the Seashells
OL,16,FFamily Hub and Millmead in Margate
OL,17,F'creates a duplication'.
OL,19,FIf plans to cut funding are approved,
OL,20,Fthe contract would come to an end in
OL,21,FMarch 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
