OL,6,F"Following the introduction of our new
OL,7,FFamily Hub model across Kent last
OL,8,Fyear, the management cost for these
OL,9,Ftwo commissioned services now creates
OL,10,Fa duplication as KCC is also paying
OL,11,Ffor the management of its in-house
OL,12,Fservices at KCC Family Hubs across the
OL,13,FDistricts of Swale and Thanet.
OL,15,F"By not renewing these contracts when
OL,16,Fthey naturally come to an end in March
OL,17,F2025, we can make a much-needed
OL,18,Fefficiency saving whilst continuing to
OL,19,Fprovide essential services for
OL,20,Ffamilies and young people in these
OL,21,Fareas.
